0005 datalen=[1e3 1e4 1e5 1e6];
0006 len=length(datalen);
0007 tsave=zeros(len,1);
0008 tload=zeros(len,1);
0009 for i=1:len
0010     tic;
0011     json=savejson('data',struct('d1',rand(datalen(i),3),'d2',rand(datalen(i),3)>0.5));
0012     tsave(i)=toc;
0013     data=loadjson(json);
0014     tload(i)=toc-tsave(i);
0015     fprintf(1,'matrix size: %d\n',datalen(i));
0016 end
